text: RhinotermesHagen HA (1858) Monographie der Termiten. Linnaea Entomologica 12: i-iii + 4-342 + 459. is a South American genus of termites typical of the family Rhinotermitidae. ==Species== The Termite CatalogueTermite Catalogue (retrieved 12 July 2019) lists the following: * Rhinotermes hispidus * Rhinotermes manni * Rhinotermes marginalis * †Rhinotermes miocenicus * Rhinotermes nasutus ==References== == External links == * Category:Termites Category:Insects of South America
title: Rhinotermes
